Package: erlr
Title: Exposure-Response Tools for Logistic Regression Models
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Danielle", "Navarro", , "djnavarro@protonmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7648-6578"))
Description:
    Provides estimation tools for exposure-response models that use
    logistic regression for binary responses: model fitting and
    prediction, stepwise covariate modelling, and simulation-based
    visual predictive checks. For a model-agnostic mini-language to
    visualise exposure-response models (including those fitted with
    erlr), see the companion package 'erplots'.
